document_data.caption: The location of Shippers' Storage (labeled 254) on a circa [[1357 DR]] map of [[Waterdeep]]
document_data.name: Shippers' Storage
document_data.aliases: Warehouse of the Fellowship of Salters, Packers, and Joiners
document_data.mainbody: '''Shippers' Storage''' was a warehouse in [[Waterdeep]] that was owned by the [[Guilds of Waterdeep|Waterdhavian guild]] known as the [[Fellowship of Salters, Packers, and Joiners]].
document_data.Location: This warehouse was located in the [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]] of Waterdeep.
document_data.Structure: This warehouse was three stories tall.
